> Teste de descricao de projeto

## Install


```sh
📂 -- src
    |-- directoryList.md
    |-- index.ts
    |-- structure.txt
    📂 -- config
        |-- generate.js
        |-- index.js
    📂 -- dist
        |-- README.md
    📂 -- functions
        |-- cli.ts
        |-- generated_arquive.ts
    📂 -- layouts
        |-- default.md
        |-- layout.md

```
